BTG Pactual Studies Acquisition of BR Malls Control, Veja Says

-- B y   H e l d e r   M a r i n h o
-- 
2011-02-12T14:48:25Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-12/btg-pactual-studies-acquisition-of-br-malls-control-veja-says.html
Banco BTG Pactual SA is studying the
acquisition of a controlling stake in  BR Malls Participacoes SA ,  Brazil ’s biggest owner of shopping malls,  Veja magazine  said in
its Radar column, without saying where it obtained the
information.  A BTG Pactual press representative, who asked not to be
identified because of internal policy, told Bloomberg News that
the Sao Paulo-based bank doesn’t comment on market speculation.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Helder Marinho in São Paulo at 
 hmarinho@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Francisco Marcelino at 
 mdeoliveira@bloomberg.net . 